Requirements
1.    Create a native-app based application to server as a basic weather app.
2.    Search Screen:
a.    Allow customer to enter a US city
b.    Call the openweathermap.org API and display the information you think a user would be interested in seeing. Be sure to have the app download and display a weather icon.
3.    Auto load the last city searched upon app launch.
Frameworks:
Looking at your application which components are generic and could be extracted and packaged into reusable component.

Technical Notes:-

Development Tools - Xcode 8.2.1
iOS SDK Used - 10.2
Programming Language - Objective C
Third party API - http://openweathermap.org/

Reference :-
http://openweathermap.org/current
http://openweathermap.org/weather-conditions
http://openweathermap.org/city/5037649

For UnitTestCase :
Should enable the project setting macro UINITTEST=1 to run the unit test
